Liverpool welcome Napoli in the Champions League on Wednesday night. The Reds currently top Group E with nine points, while the Serie A side are second with eight. Napoli won the reverse fixture 2-0 and the holders will be seeking revenge on home soil. Kick off is 9pm West African time. Wednesday, November 27
